rows.label: tlk45350153_01_msg0001
rows.name:
The Divine Beast weapons Superbia
possesses are necessary to defend
ourselves against the Invidian threat.

rows.label: tlk45350153_01_msg0002
rows.name:
The four-legged Divine Beast weapon just
over there, known as Tortoga, was
completed by my great predecessor.

rows.label: tlk45350153_01_msg0003
rows.name:
We created one called Cetus
just recently, as well.

rows.label: tlk45350153_01_msg0004
rows.name:
We researchers work tirelessly day and
night to develop these creations.

rows.label: tlk45350153_01_msg0005
rows.name:
Right now, we're trying to enhance the
capabilities of the flying type.
